WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 9=

00:01:41.460 --> 00:01:42.370 line:80%
Tomorrow morning,

00:01:42.490 --> 00:01:43.930 line:80%
go back to Qingque Sect on your own.

00:01:46.370 --> 00:01:47.210 line:80%
What about you?

00:01:47.620 --> 00:01:49.300 line:80%
You already figured out
how to break this.

00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:52.210 line:80%
Guangtian Sect and Lord Song
will support you.

00:01:52.620 --> 00:01:53.460 line:80%
I'm guessing

00:01:53.930 --> 00:01:55.930 line:80%
you've already got a plan in mind.

00:01:57.620 --> 00:01:58.730 line:80%
Yeah, I have.

00:02:02.570 --> 00:02:03.410 line:80%
Zhao,

00:02:03.820 --> 00:02:05.060 line:80%
what do you mean?

00:02:05.370 --> 00:02:07.180 line:80%
Yin Dai imprisoned Elder Kaiyang

00:02:07.810 --> 00:02:09.650 line:80%
to get the Ziwei Method.

00:02:10.140 --> 00:02:11.530 line:80%
When you read Yin Dai's handbook,

00:02:11.810 --> 00:02:13.340 line:80%
you already saw it

00:02:14.370 --> 00:02:15.930 line:80%
in its hidden layer,

00:02:16.210 --> 00:02:17.050 line:80%
right?

00:02:17.950 --> 00:02:19.740 line:80%
The fire's dying down.
I'll go get some more.

00:02:19.740 --> 00:02:20.580 line:80%
I'll do it.

00:02:25.420 --> 00:02:28.860 line:80%
(Ziwei Method)

00:02:33.620 --> 00:02:34.460 line:80%
What did you see?

00:02:37.260 --> 00:02:38.300 line:80%
That's why you're looking

00:02:38.300 --> 00:02:39.620 line:80%
for Yin Dai's handbook, right?

00:02:42.180 --> 00:02:43.420 line:80%
Back in the Library dungeon,

00:02:43.431 --> 00:02:45.460 line:80%
Qian Xueshen said that the antidote
was the saliva.

00:02:45.900 --> 00:02:47.220 line:80%
Saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:49.020 line:80%
Where is it?

00:02:49.180 --> 00:02:50.980 line:80%
In the snow mountains
in the Freezing Area.

00:02:51.380 --> 00:02:52.220 line:80%
From that moment,

00:02:52.420 --> 00:02:53.980 line:80%
you already had a plan

00:02:54.220 --> 00:02:55.620 line:80%
to look for the saliva.

00:02:55.620 --> 00:02:57.620 line:80%
The handbook must contain records

00:02:57.980 --> 00:03:00.300 line:80%
that the saliva is one of the key media

00:03:00.300 --> 00:03:01.660 line:80%
for cultivating the Ziwei Method.

00:03:03.060 --> 00:03:04.340 line:80%
You waited for me

00:03:04.860 --> 00:03:06.746 line:80%
and chased me all the way
to the snow mountains

00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:09.220 line:80%
just to use me to find the saliva.

00:03:12.020 --> 00:03:13.286 line:80%
You deliberately got close to me

00:03:13.947 --> 00:03:15.360 line:80%
and helped me every step of the way,

00:03:16.380 --> 00:03:17.900 line:80%
all for the Ziwei Method.

00:03:23.380 --> 00:03:24.220 line:80%
That's right.

00:03:24.900 --> 00:03:27.460 line:80%
I went to Qingque Sect
for the Ziwei Method.

00:03:28.660 --> 00:03:30.700 line:80%
But since you already suspected me,

00:03:31.006 --> 00:03:33.372 line:80%
why did you still let me go
to the snow mountains with you?

00:03:37.220 --> 00:03:38.060 line:80%
That's because...

00:03:41.100 --> 00:03:42.100 line:80%
Because you clung to me.

00:03:45.180 --> 00:03:46.620 line:80%
With your intelligence and sharpness,

00:03:46.820 --> 00:03:48.013 line:80%
if you wanted to shake me off,

00:03:48.220 --> 00:03:49.900 line:80%
wouldn't that have been easy?

00:03:50.300 --> 00:03:51.060 line:80%
You already guessed

00:03:51.071 --> 00:03:53.293 line:80%
that some of the companions
were from the demonic sect.

00:03:53.304 --> 00:03:55.064 line:80%
You knew this journey was dangerous,

00:03:55.660 --> 00:03:57.380 line:80%
so you wanted me to protect you

00:03:57.380 --> 00:03:58.780 line:80%
and help you find the saliva asap.

00:03:59.460 --> 00:04:00.540 line:80%
That way,

00:04:00.780 --> 00:04:01.860 line:80%
you were using me too.

00:04:02.340 --> 00:04:03.860 line:80%
There's no difference between us.

00:04:04.313 --> 00:04:05.980 line:80%
You know the consequences
of Nie Hengcheng

00:04:05.980 --> 00:04:07.186 line:80%
cultivating the Ziwei Method.

00:04:07.260 --> 00:04:08.910 line:80%
If you'll become a second Nie Hengcheng,

00:04:08.910 --> 00:04:09.780 line:80%
I might as well...

00:04:09.780 --> 00:04:10.620 line:80%
What?

00:04:11.980 --> 00:04:12.860 line:80%
Kill me?

00:04:16.860 --> 00:04:18.306 line:80%
I might as well lock you up right now

00:04:18.460 --> 00:04:19.740 line:80%
to avoid future trouble.

00:04:20.220 --> 00:04:21.060 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:21.660 --> 00:04:22.900 line:80%
I will never

00:04:22.900 --> 00:04:24.180 line:80%
let anyone lock me up again.

00:04:26.340 --> 00:04:27.860 line:80%
Perhaps it won't be long

00:04:29.640 --> 00:04:31.340 line:80%
before I put your mind at ease.

00:05:07.340 --> 00:05:08.260 line:80%
Mu Qingyan?

00:05:13.660 --> 00:05:14.980 line:80%
The saliva hasn't decreased.

00:05:15.460 --> 00:05:16.340 line:80%
Mu Qingyan?

00:05:17.300 --> 00:05:18.260 line:80%
Miss, you're awake.

00:05:18.940 --> 00:05:19.780 line:80%
Come.

00:05:20.660 --> 00:05:21.780 line:80%
Come eat some wonton.

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:24.940 line:80%
He knocked me out

00:05:25.580 --> 00:05:26.933 line:80%
and just gave me a bowl of wonton?

00:05:27.020 --> 00:05:28.500 line:80%
Uncle Cheng, where is he?

00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:30.500 line:80%
The Young Master said

00:05:30.820 --> 00:05:32.340 line:80%
you were exhausted from traveling

00:05:32.340 --> 00:05:33.340 line:80%
and should sleep soundly

00:05:33.580 --> 00:05:35.260 line:80%
before you return to Qingque Sect.

00:05:36.140 --> 00:05:37.260 line:80%
He went back for revenge?

00:05:38.900 --> 00:05:39.740 line:80%
The Young Master said

00:05:39.907 --> 00:05:41.896 line:80%
the debts of the Mu clan
across three generations

00:05:42.100 --> 00:05:43.860 line:80%
should be settled with Nie.

00:05:45.540 --> 00:05:46.540 line:80%
I knew it.

00:05:46.860 --> 00:05:48.140 line:80%
With his temperament,

00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:50.420 line:80%
he was bound to reclaim
the Chief position.

00:05:54.260 --> 00:05:55.860 line:80%
If he didn't want the saliva,

00:05:56.700 --> 00:05:58.460 line:80%
why did he go
to the snow mountains with me?

00:05:59.020 --> 00:06:00.620 line:80%
He even risked his life.

00:06:00.940 --> 00:06:01.940 line:80%
He said

00:06:02.226 --> 00:06:03.580 line:80%
he couldn't let you be alone there,

00:06:03.580 --> 00:06:05.100 line:80%
without anyone to rely on.

00:06:05.420 --> 00:06:07.580 line:80%
He couldn't let you
gamble your life alone.

00:06:08.180 --> 00:06:09.860 line:80%
You took care of the Young Master

00:06:09.860 --> 00:06:11.660 line:80%
for many days at Qingque Sect.

00:06:12.300 --> 00:06:14.482 line:80%
He made the wonton before he left,

00:06:14.493 --> 00:06:15.860 line:80%
served with ginseng chicken soup.

00:06:15.860 --> 00:06:17.100 line:80%
Eat them while they're hot.

00:06:28.100 --> 00:06:29.100 line:80%
Uncle Cheng,

00:06:31.220 --> 00:06:33.100 line:80%
why is there no scallion?

00:06:40.660 --> 00:06:41.500 line:80%
Thank you.

00:06:48.100 --> 00:06:50.020 line:80%
You complain for three days

00:06:50.166 --> 00:06:51.713 line:80%
just because a wonton has no scallions.

00:06:52.060 --> 00:06:54.660 line:80%
Someone so attached to worldly pleasures

00:06:56.060 --> 00:06:58.660 line:80%
could hardly last three days

00:06:59.260 --> 00:07:00.580 line:80%
on this cold, silent snow peak.

00:07:00.933 --> 00:07:02.380 line:80%
And you want to live here long-term?

00:07:05.180 --> 00:07:06.020 line:80%
Uncle Cheng,

00:07:06.860 --> 00:07:07.820 line:80%
if someone...

00:07:09.180 --> 00:07:10.460 line:80%
I mean, a friend of mine.

00:07:11.540 --> 00:07:14.020 line:80%
If she doesn't get wonton
with scallions,

00:07:14.780 --> 00:07:16.620 line:80%
she'll be angry for days.

00:07:17.860 --> 00:07:19.740 line:80%
Does that count as petty?

00:07:21.780 --> 00:07:23.220 line:80%
By common sense,

00:07:23.660 --> 00:07:25.340 line:80%
that would indeed be petty.

00:07:31.660 --> 00:07:32.580 line:80%
The Young Master

00:07:33.540 --> 00:07:35.060 line:80%
ordered me to give this token

00:07:35.220 --> 00:07:36.260 line:80%
to you.

00:07:39.620 --> 00:07:41.140 line:80%
(Aide)
Aide of Bliss Palace?

00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:42.860 line:80%
Against the Demonic Camp,

00:07:43.220 --> 00:07:45.300 line:80%
this item may be of help.

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:47.140 line:80%
Miss,

00:07:47.140 --> 00:07:48.180 line:80%
be extra careful.

00:07:53.740 --> 00:07:56.140 line:80%
(Aide)

00:07:59.260 --> 00:08:00.660 line:80%
It's too hot!

00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:02.940 line:80%
Sorry, sorry.

00:08:03.260 --> 00:08:04.420 line:80%
Sorry to disturb you.

00:08:08.420 --> 00:08:11.100 line:80%
(Aide)

00:08:11.100 --> 00:08:13.340 line:80%
Mocking me before leaving?

00:08:13.940 --> 00:08:14.820 line:80%
You're the petty one.

00:08:14.820 --> 00:08:16.140 line:80%
Your whole family is petty.

00:08:31.620 --> 00:08:33.140 line:80%
News from the mountain foot:

00:08:33.660 --> 00:08:36.300 line:80%
Reinforcements from Xuankong Nunnery
and Peiqiong Manor

00:08:36.300 --> 00:08:37.460 line:80%
were blocked halfway.

00:08:39.340 --> 00:08:41.100 line:80%
The demonic sect prepared in advance.

00:08:41.740 --> 00:08:43.460 line:80%
If we just wait here,

00:08:43.660 --> 00:08:44.980 line:80%
that won't solve anything.

00:08:55.300 --> 00:08:56.540 line:80%
It's been 15 days.

00:08:57.900 --> 00:08:59.180 line:80%
I don't know

00:08:59.300 --> 00:09:00.660 line:80%
how Zhao is doing now.

00:09:16.220 --> 00:09:17.060 line:80%
Fengchi,

00:09:17.620 --> 00:09:19.460 line:80%
you brought all the juniors here.

00:09:20.420 --> 00:09:21.420 line:80%
What advice do you have?

00:09:22.540 --> 00:09:23.420 line:80%
Lord Song.

00:09:24.020 --> 00:09:25.100 line:80%
May I ask

00:09:25.700 --> 00:09:27.660 line:80%
how much longer Guangtian Sect

00:09:27.660 --> 00:09:28.940 line:80%
will be guarding Qingque Sect?

00:09:30.220 --> 00:09:31.060 line:80%
Uncle,

00:09:31.700 --> 00:09:33.940 line:80%
I know you want to protect us,

00:09:34.340 --> 00:09:35.820 line:80%
but it's already been half a month.

00:09:36.260 --> 00:09:38.186 line:80%
We're confined
to the Disciples' Dorm every day.

00:09:38.660 --> 00:09:41.180 line:80%
Even my mother's guards
were ordered back when they tried

00:09:41.460 --> 00:09:42.860 line:80%
to go buy necessities.

00:09:43.980 --> 00:09:44.820 line:80%
Uncle,

00:09:45.380 --> 00:09:47.620 line:80%
you don't even trust us?

00:09:47.620 --> 00:09:48.580 line:80%
It's not that.

00:09:48.780 --> 00:09:49.620 line:80%
I think

00:09:50.060 --> 00:09:51.820 line:80%
they want to take over Qingque Sect.

00:09:51.820 --> 00:09:52.700 line:80%
Fengchi.

00:09:55.860 --> 00:09:57.540 line:80%
The Qingque Sect

00:09:58.740 --> 00:09:59.860 line:80%
is not in chaos yet.

00:10:00.100 --> 00:10:00.980 line:80%
If so,

00:10:01.500 --> 00:10:02.940 line:80%
why are we being confined here,

00:10:03.180 --> 00:10:05.460 line:80%
letting Guangtian Sect
overstep its bounds?

00:10:05.860 --> 00:10:06.700 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:10:06.860 --> 00:10:09.229 line:80%
are you pretending not to know,

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.420 line:80%
or are you secretly pleased,

00:10:10.420 --> 00:10:11.740 line:80%
hoping your father

00:10:11.740 --> 00:10:13.020 line:80%
could become the Lord?

00:10:18.220 --> 00:10:19.060 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:10:21.220 --> 00:10:22.060 line:80%
Lord Song,

00:10:22.660 --> 00:10:24.180 line:80%
why get mad when I'm telling the truth?

00:10:24.700 --> 00:10:26.540 line:80%
Even if there truly were a Body Shift,

00:10:26.540 --> 00:10:28.340 line:80%
interrogating everyone one by one

00:10:28.540 --> 00:10:30.900 line:80%
for half a month
would reveal the traitor.

00:10:31.340 --> 00:10:32.180 line:80%
But what about now?

00:10:33.260 --> 00:10:34.380 line:80%
You sit still and do nothing,

00:10:34.660 --> 00:10:36.700 line:80%
letting Guangtian Sect
make the decisions.

00:10:36.980 --> 00:10:38.220 line:80%
What is your intention?

00:10:38.580 --> 00:10:39.620 line:80%
Dai,

00:10:40.260 --> 00:10:42.340 line:80%
if not for the brotherhood

00:10:42.580 --> 00:10:44.020 line:80%
I shared with your late father,

00:10:44.620 --> 00:10:47.289 line:80%
I'd kill you for your master

00:10:47.300 --> 00:10:48.740 line:80%
just for slandering fellow disciples

00:10:48.750 --> 00:10:49.590 line:80%
and spreading alarm.

00:10:49.590 --> 00:10:50.450 line:80%
Father.

00:10:52.340 --> 00:10:53.180 line:80%
Fengchi,

00:10:53.740 --> 00:10:55.260 line:80%
my family harbors no ulterior motives.

00:10:55.413 --> 00:10:56.542 line:80%
Once this matter is resolved,

00:10:56.553 --> 00:10:57.940 line:80%
Guangtian Sect will withdraw.

00:10:58.620 --> 00:11:00.100 line:80%
If you are still uneasy,

00:11:02.420 --> 00:11:03.580 line:80%
I will also leave the sect.

00:11:03.940 --> 00:11:05.020 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:11:05.740 --> 00:11:07.300 line:80%
that's not what I meant.

00:11:09.180 --> 00:11:10.860 line:80%
You know Master values you,

00:11:10.980 --> 00:11:12.100 line:80%
and Lingbo depends on you.

00:11:12.220 --> 00:11:14.380 line:80%
Why put on such a show?

00:11:17.660 --> 00:11:18.660 line:80%
Foolish.

00:11:20.500 --> 00:11:22.300 line:80%
I act openly and uprightly.

00:11:22.740 --> 00:11:25.180 line:80%
I won't stoop to argue
with an ignorant brat like you.

00:11:26.740 --> 00:11:27.580 line:80%
Fine.

00:11:28.340 --> 00:11:29.340 line:80%
Let me tell you.

00:11:29.806 --> 00:11:31.313 line:80%
The reason you're not allowed to leave

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:34.300 line:80%
is that I don't want outsiders to know

00:11:34.500 --> 00:11:36.900 line:80%
that your master,
the Lord of the top set,

00:11:38.020 --> 00:11:40.460 line:80%
was swapped by demonic sect scum.

00:11:42.340 --> 00:11:43.940 line:80%
If this leaks out,

00:11:44.340 --> 00:11:46.020 line:80%
how will the Six Sects

00:11:46.260 --> 00:11:48.500 line:80%
ever hold their heads up
in Jianghu again?

00:11:48.780 --> 00:11:49.620 line:80%
Uncle,

00:11:50.460 --> 00:11:52.620 line:80%
it's impossible to swap an elite
like my father.

00:11:53.660 --> 00:11:54.620 line:80%
Lord Song

00:11:55.180 --> 00:11:56.780 line:80%
is merely taking advantage of us

00:11:56.940 --> 00:11:58.700 line:80%
to reap the benefits.

00:11:58.700 --> 00:11:59.540 line:80%
Enough.

00:12:05.380 --> 00:12:06.860 line:80%
Yuzhi is still recovering.

00:12:06.860 --> 00:12:08.100 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:12:08.700 --> 00:12:09.540 line:80%
All of you, go back.

00:12:10.620 --> 00:12:11.740 line:80%
Yes, Lady Yin.

00:12:18.620 --> 00:12:19.460 line:80%
Shijun,

00:12:20.380 --> 00:12:22.100 line:80%
the juniors were reckless.

00:12:22.500 --> 00:12:23.780 line:80%
Please don't take it to heart.

00:12:26.180 --> 00:12:27.740 line:80%
With troubles both within and without,

00:12:28.420 --> 00:12:29.860 line:80%
we trouble you

00:12:29.980 --> 00:12:31.780 line:80%
to help manage sect affairs.

00:12:32.260 --> 00:12:33.180 line:80%
But may I ask

00:12:33.660 --> 00:12:35.540 line:80%
what your plans are next?

00:12:35.540 --> 00:12:37.300 line:80%
Zhao has gone to find the antidote.

00:12:37.500 --> 00:12:38.820 line:80%
Let's wait for her return.

00:12:38.980 --> 00:12:39.820 line:80%
Uncle,

00:12:40.100 --> 00:12:41.580 line:80%
you trust her that much?

00:12:44.673 --> 00:12:45.740 line:80%
Reinforcements are blocked.

00:12:46.133 --> 00:12:47.380 line:80%
Master's identity is uncertain.

00:12:48.740 --> 00:12:50.420 line:80%
Right now, we can only wait for Zhao.

00:12:51.100 --> 00:12:53.300 line:80%
You really think Cai Zhao
can find the antidote?

00:12:53.860 --> 00:12:54.700 line:80%
Maybe by now

00:12:54.820 --> 00:12:55.860 line:80%
she's already run off

00:12:55.860 --> 00:12:57.660 line:80%
with that mysterious Chang Ning.

00:13:01.060 --> 00:13:01.900 line:80%
Shijun,

00:13:03.820 --> 00:13:06.740 line:80%
Cai Zhao is just a junior.

00:13:07.020 --> 00:13:08.860 line:80%
We can't rely solely on her.

00:13:09.260 --> 00:13:10.100 line:80%
Zhao...

00:13:10.100 --> 00:13:11.540 line:80%
Zhao!

00:13:11.700 --> 00:13:13.540 line:80%
Zhao...

00:13:13.540 --> 00:13:14.700 line:80%
Lady Yin.

00:13:14.940 --> 00:13:15.820 line:80%
Speak.

00:13:15.820 --> 00:13:17.020 line:80%
We received a pigeon message.

00:13:17.380 --> 00:13:18.220 line:80%
Zhao has found

00:13:18.780 --> 00:13:19.980 line:80%
the antidote and returned.

00:13:20.420 --> 00:13:21.740 line:80%
She's arrived in Qingque Town.

00:13:41.500 --> 00:13:42.980 line:80%
- Xingjia.
- Zhao.

00:13:42.980 --> 00:13:43.940 line:80%
How is the situation

00:13:43.940 --> 00:13:44.900 line:80%
on the mountain now?

00:13:46.040 --> 00:13:47.571 line:80%
Thousandfold Cliff is currently guarded

00:13:47.582 --> 00:13:48.806 line:80%
by Guangtian Sect and Uncle Li.

00:13:48.900 --> 00:13:50.940 line:80%
Other than me
purchasing supplies by order,

00:13:51.100 --> 00:13:52.260 line:80%
no one is allowed in or out.

00:13:52.740 --> 00:13:53.373 line:80%
The demonic sect

00:13:53.384 --> 00:13:55.115 line:80%
doesn't know the situation
on the mountain,

00:13:55.126 --> 00:13:56.307 line:80%
so they don't dare act rashly.

00:13:58.420 --> 00:13:59.740 line:80%
I secretly investigated for days.

00:14:00.066 --> 00:14:01.060 line:80%
At least over 100 members

00:14:01.060 --> 00:14:02.980 line:80%
of the Demonic Camp
are hiding in the town.

00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:05.420 line:80%
Their leader is a mysterious,
cloaked figure.

00:14:05.420 --> 00:14:06.366 line:80%
His face can't be seen.

00:14:06.460 --> 00:14:08.740 line:80%
I don't know if he is their leader,
Lu Chengnan.

00:14:08.980 --> 00:14:10.540 line:80%
Yuzhi feared for your safety,

00:14:10.540 --> 00:14:11.953 line:80%
so he asked me to wait here for you.

00:14:13.700 --> 00:14:15.380 line:80%
Dissolve this bottle of saliva in water,

00:14:15.380 --> 00:14:16.700 line:80%
and it will undo the Body Shift.

00:14:17.100 --> 00:14:17.940 line:80%
Is this enough?

00:14:18.060 --> 00:14:18.980 line:80%
Yes.

00:14:18.980 --> 00:14:19.820 line:80%
Okay, I'll head back.

00:14:19.980 --> 00:14:20.820 line:80%
Wait.

00:14:22.300 --> 00:14:24.720 line:80%
Once the demonic sect knows
the Body Shift has been exposed,

00:14:24.740 --> 00:14:27.060 line:80%
Master will lose his value.

00:14:27.340 --> 00:14:28.180 line:80%
Maybe

00:14:28.820 --> 00:14:30.620 line:80%
his life will be in danger.

00:14:30.793 --> 00:14:31.740 line:80%
Then what should we do?

00:14:32.300 --> 00:14:34.060 line:80%
Give this saliva to Yuzhi.

00:14:34.980 --> 00:14:36.980 line:80%
Expose the impostor
on the mountain first.

00:14:37.260 --> 00:14:38.860 line:80%
I have my own way to find master.

00:14:39.740 --> 00:14:40.620 line:80%
What way?

00:14:40.900 --> 00:14:41.740 line:80%
Just trust me.

00:14:43.020 --> 00:14:43.940 line:80%
Be careful.

00:15:33.526 --> 00:15:34.733 line:80%
The Lord is still in seclusion.

00:15:35.180 --> 00:15:36.020 line:80%
He won't see anyone.

00:15:52.700 --> 00:15:53.980 line:80%
Weren't you told not to come?

00:15:55.220 --> 00:15:56.580 line:80%
I am you're wife.

00:15:56.940 --> 00:15:57.900 line:80%
I'm going in.

00:15:58.460 --> 00:15:59.420 line:80%
Who dares stop me?

00:15:59.693 --> 00:16:01.380 line:80%
Not letting you come
is for your own good.

00:16:01.780 --> 00:16:02.660 line:80%
Right now,

00:16:02.660 --> 00:16:03.900 line:80%
this is a time of turmoil.

00:16:05.020 --> 00:16:07.460 line:80%
You should rest in Double Lotus Palace.

00:16:07.580 --> 00:16:09.060 line:80%
Don't come out again.

00:16:09.580 --> 00:16:10.660 line:80%
You're always like this.

00:16:11.060 --> 00:16:13.500 line:80%
Whenever something happens,
you make me hide away.

00:16:14.260 --> 00:16:15.780 line:80%
It makes me look utterly useless.

00:16:16.020 --> 00:16:17.060 line:80%
That's not what I mean.

00:16:17.740 --> 00:16:19.300 line:80%
I know you want to protect me,

00:16:19.620 --> 00:16:21.820 line:80%
but I'm your wife.

00:16:22.300 --> 00:16:23.500 line:80%
We share honor

00:16:23.700 --> 00:16:24.740 line:80%
and disgrace alike.

00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:27.660 line:80%
When trouble comes,
we should face it together.

00:16:28.100 --> 00:16:30.220 line:80%
How can I always rely on you?

00:16:31.260 --> 00:16:32.420 line:80%
At this critical moment,

00:16:32.700 --> 00:16:34.420 line:80%
with the demonic sect
watching from outside

00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:36.300 line:80%
and villains sowing suspicion within,

00:16:36.660 --> 00:16:37.740 line:80%
nothing can happen to you.

00:16:38.580 --> 00:16:41.540 line:80%
I heard your poison injury has relapsed.

00:16:42.180 --> 00:16:43.580 line:80%
Even Xiuming's medicine

00:16:44.060 --> 00:16:45.300 line:80%
has been ineffective.

00:16:48.860 --> 00:16:50.220 line:80%
What's in this box

00:16:50.380 --> 00:16:51.860 line:80%
was gifted by an old friend.

00:16:52.220 --> 00:16:54.620 line:80%
I preserved it in cold ice for years.

00:16:55.300 --> 00:16:57.660 line:80%
I didn't even take it out

00:16:57.660 --> 00:16:59.180 line:80%
when Yuzhi was injured.

00:17:04.620 --> 00:17:06.340 line:80%
Back then, this old friend

00:17:06.700 --> 00:17:08.500 line:80%
traveled through beaches and ravines,

00:17:08.780 --> 00:17:10.460 line:80%
deep into deserts and miasma forests,

00:17:11.020 --> 00:17:12.660 line:80%
risking countless dangers,

00:17:13.340 --> 00:17:14.900 line:80%
just to refine

00:17:15.660 --> 00:17:16.940 line:80%
one Clearing Pill.

00:17:19.020 --> 00:17:20.180 line:80%
It's said this medicine

00:17:20.580 --> 00:17:22.060 line:80%
can warm sinews and activate meridians

00:17:22.180 --> 00:17:23.180 line:80%
and enhance cultivation.

00:17:23.420 --> 00:17:24.540 line:80%
It's truly rare in the world.

00:17:26.940 --> 00:17:27.780 line:80%
Yunke,

00:17:28.660 --> 00:17:30.340 line:80%
this medicine will surely help you

00:17:31.060 --> 00:17:32.460 line:80%
recover completely.

00:17:33.180 --> 00:17:34.580 line:80%
Take it now.

00:17:35.220 --> 00:17:36.060 line:80%
Dear,

00:17:36.740 --> 00:17:37.940 line:80%
I just took another pill.

00:17:38.540 --> 00:17:39.420 line:80%
I'll take this

00:17:40.540 --> 00:17:41.380 line:80%
later.

00:17:46.860 --> 00:17:47.700 line:80%
Yunke.

00:17:48.700 --> 00:17:49.940 line:80%
I'm willing

00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:51.580 line:80%
to weather storms with you.

00:17:53.260 --> 00:17:54.540 line:80%
Will you trust me?

00:17:58.540 --> 00:17:59.380 line:80%
Yes.

00:17:59.820 --> 00:18:00.660 line:80%
I trust you.

00:18:22.940 --> 00:18:23.780 line:80%
Hurry.

00:18:32.380 --> 00:18:33.460 line:80%
Zhuang.

00:18:33.460 --> 00:18:34.300 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:18:49.980 --> 00:18:50.820 line:80%
Dalou.

00:18:54.660 --> 00:18:55.500 line:80%
Dalou.

00:18:57.060 --> 00:18:57.900 line:80%
Master.

00:18:58.860 --> 00:18:59.700 line:80%
Where is Master?

00:19:03.060 --> 00:19:03.900 line:80%
Dalou.

00:19:04.180 --> 00:19:05.020 line:80%
Dalou.

00:19:11.620 --> 00:19:13.340 line:80%
Sorry, we're closed for the day.

00:19:13.340 --> 00:19:14.300 line:80%
(Aide)

00:19:14.940 --> 00:19:15.780 line:80%
The aide token.

00:19:17.300 --> 00:19:18.980 line:80%
Greetings, Aide.

00:19:19.540 --> 00:19:21.380 line:80%
News from Thousandfold Cliff
has been sealed.

00:19:21.580 --> 00:19:23.220 line:80%
The Chief fears something wrong

00:19:23.420 --> 00:19:24.940 line:80%
and ordered me to escort the hostages

00:19:25.380 --> 00:19:26.820 line:80%
to Hanhai Mountains

00:19:27.580 --> 00:19:28.780 line:80%
for disposal by Bliss Palace.

00:19:29.340 --> 00:19:30.740 line:80%
But the strategist ordered

00:19:30.740 --> 00:19:32.300 line:80%
that no one may approach the hostages.

00:19:34.700 --> 00:19:35.940 line:80%
By the Chief's order,

00:19:37.620 --> 00:19:39.380 line:80%
you dare disobey?

00:19:39.940 --> 00:19:41.100 line:80%
We wouldn't dare.

00:19:41.700 --> 00:19:43.660 line:80%
But we still need
to report to the strategist.

00:19:46.380 --> 00:19:48.420 line:80%
You're putting the strategist
before the Chief?

00:19:48.780 --> 00:19:49.860 line:80%
Are you plotting rebellion?

00:19:49.959 --> 00:19:51.266 line:80%
- Of course not.
- Of course not.

00:19:52.220 --> 00:19:53.060 line:80%
Lead the way at once.

00:19:53.180 --> 00:19:54.020 line:80%
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:19:54.420 --> 00:19:55.260 line:80%
This way, please.

00:20:10.700 --> 00:20:11.540 line:80%
Which one?

00:20:16.820 --> 00:20:17.780 line:80%
Leave me.

00:20:22.060 --> 00:20:22.940 line:80%
Didn't you hear me?

00:20:23.180 --> 00:20:24.020 line:80%
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:20:47.060 --> 00:20:47.900 line:80%
Master.

00:20:58.660 --> 00:20:59.500 line:80%
Master?

00:21:04.260 --> 00:21:05.100 line:80%
Qinong.

00:21:06.380 --> 00:21:08.580 line:80%
What are you doing here,
instead of watching

00:21:09.260 --> 00:21:10.540 line:80%
Chen Shu find the saliva?

00:21:14.980 --> 00:21:16.980 line:80%
I'm acting on the Chief's orders

00:21:18.340 --> 00:21:19.420 line:80%
to take your life.

00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:26.540 line:80%
Master.

00:21:44.100 --> 00:21:45.020 line:80%
Don't pursue.

00:21:46.420 --> 00:21:47.340 line:80%
Let's go back now.

00:22:00.420 --> 00:22:02.180 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
Shijun,

00:22:02.380 --> 00:22:03.700 line:80%
what do you mean by this?

00:22:04.580 --> 00:22:06.340 line:80%
You're a fake lord.

00:22:06.340 --> 00:22:07.660 line:80%
Who exactly are you?

00:22:07.780 --> 00:22:10.060 line:80%
Hurry up and reveal your true form.

00:22:10.500 --> 00:22:11.820 line:80%
We can talk things out.

00:22:12.740 --> 00:22:13.700 line:80%
Shijun,

00:22:14.420 --> 00:22:15.740 line:80%
what nonsense are you spouting?

00:22:16.500 --> 00:22:18.100 line:80%
Don't let the demonic sect deceive you

00:22:18.420 --> 00:22:21.460 line:80%
and damage the friendship
between the two sects.

00:22:21.660 --> 00:22:23.100 line:80%
Then we'll strip off your fake skin.

00:22:30.060 --> 00:22:30.900 line:80%
Master.

00:22:31.940 --> 00:22:33.820 line:80%
The real one has returned.

00:22:33.820 --> 00:22:35.060 line:80%
You counterfeit

00:22:35.060 --> 00:22:36.620 line:80%
should stop resisting stubbornly.

00:22:40.740 --> 00:22:41.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:22:43.100 --> 00:22:44.780 line:80%
did you take Qian Xueshen away

00:22:45.060 --> 00:22:48.580 line:80%
just to fabricate a fake master?

00:22:49.980 --> 00:22:51.020 line:80%
How shameless.

00:22:51.580 --> 00:22:53.060 line:80%
Your talent for turning the tables

00:22:53.071 --> 00:22:54.494 line:80%
is even better than a storyteller's.

00:22:54.580 --> 00:22:55.780 line:80%
To tell who's the real one,

00:22:56.180 --> 00:22:57.580 line:80%
you can both drink

00:22:57.900 --> 00:22:58.820 line:80%
the antidote.

00:23:04.300 --> 00:23:05.660 line:80%
This isn't an antidote

00:23:06.180 --> 00:23:07.300 line:80%
but poison.

00:23:07.740 --> 00:23:08.820 line:80%
Dodging the issue

00:23:08.940 --> 00:23:09.980 line:80%
only raises more suspicion.

00:23:10.500 --> 00:23:11.900 line:80%
Please, you two,

00:23:12.220 --> 00:23:13.300 line:80%
drink it together.

00:23:14.620 --> 00:23:15.660 line:80%
Wenxun,

00:23:17.060 --> 00:23:18.860 line:80%
you don't even trust me now?

00:23:20.260 --> 00:23:21.740 line:80%
Back then in the great war,

00:23:22.380 --> 00:23:23.220 line:80%
who carried you

00:23:23.580 --> 00:23:25.780 line:80%
out of a pile of corpses?

00:23:28.020 --> 00:23:29.180 line:80%
This farce

00:23:29.420 --> 00:23:30.380 line:80%
has gone on long enough.

00:23:30.580 --> 00:23:32.300 line:80%
If you truly think I'm fake,

00:23:32.313 --> 00:23:33.700 line:80%
invite the heads of the Six Sects

00:23:33.860 --> 00:23:35.500 line:80%
and all righteous figures of Jianghu

00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:36.940 line:80%
to Qingque Sect.

00:23:37.300 --> 00:23:38.220 line:80%
When that time comes,

00:23:38.580 --> 00:23:39.740 line:80%
right and wrong

00:23:39.940 --> 00:23:41.220 line:80%
will judge themselves.

00:23:41.460 --> 00:23:42.620 line:80%
Qiu,

00:24:01.940 --> 00:24:02.860 line:80%
this Clearing Pill

00:24:03.580 --> 00:24:05.500 line:80%
will surely help you recover.

00:24:05.620 --> 00:24:07.020 line:80%
Hurry and take it.

00:24:23.500 --> 00:24:24.700 line:80%
Long time no see.

00:24:25.100 --> 00:24:26.100 line:80%
I hope you've been well.

00:24:40.420 --> 00:24:43.380 line:80%
(Qiu Renjie, Qingque Sect)

00:24:43.860 --> 00:24:44.780 line:80%
Qiu?

00:24:47.780 --> 00:24:49.020 line:80%
Qiu Renjie?

00:24:50.940 --> 00:24:53.180 line:80%
You guessed it was me.

00:24:53.460 --> 00:24:55.820 line:80%
Thank you for gifting me
the Clearing Pill.

00:25:01.620 --> 00:25:07.420 line:80%
(Young Yin Sulian, Qingque Sect)

00:25:07.500 --> 00:25:11.260 line:80%
(Young Qiu Renjie, Qingque Sect)

00:25:18.933 --> 00:25:19.980 line:80%
This is the Clearing Pill.

00:25:20.300 --> 00:25:22.139 line:80%
It replenishes marrow
and boosts cultivation.

00:25:22.260 --> 00:25:23.380 line:80%
When you practice,

00:25:23.820 --> 00:25:25.273 line:80%
you'll make advancements more easily.

00:25:26.420 --> 00:25:27.260 line:80%
Qiu,

00:25:27.380 --> 00:25:28.220 line:80%
you're so kind.

00:25:31.860 --> 00:25:33.100 line:80%
You neither ate nor drank.

00:25:33.500 --> 00:25:35.060 line:80%
If I didn't resort to this method,

00:25:35.420 --> 00:25:37.260 line:80%
how could I expose your true face?

00:25:43.860 --> 00:25:45.820 line:80%
You still chose him.

00:25:51.220 --> 00:25:52.060 line:80%
Qiu,

00:25:52.540 --> 00:25:54.060 line:80%
you disappeared for many years.

00:25:54.660 --> 00:25:56.460 line:80%
We all thought you were dead.

00:25:56.700 --> 00:25:57.820 line:80%
Since you're alive,

00:25:57.820 --> 00:25:59.220 line:80%
why didn't you return?

00:25:59.380 --> 00:26:01.700 line:80%
Why collude with the demonic sect

00:26:02.060 --> 00:26:04.100 line:80%
and commit such fratricidal acts?

00:26:04.740 --> 00:26:06.020 line:80%
Fratricidal?

00:26:09.740 --> 00:26:10.660 line:80%
Qi Yunke,

00:26:11.380 --> 00:26:14.220 line:80%
you stole my position
and took my fiancée.

00:26:14.700 --> 00:26:17.180 line:80%
Whose brother would be like that?

00:26:18.540 --> 00:26:19.380 line:80%
Qiu,

00:26:20.180 --> 00:26:23.420 line:80%
if you're resentful about losing to me,

00:26:23.420 --> 00:26:25.820 line:80%
I'm willing to compete with you again.

00:26:28.220 --> 00:26:31.860 line:80%
You really are the one
that Yin Dai favored.

00:26:32.020 --> 00:26:34.620 line:80%
What a hypocrite.

00:26:35.260 --> 00:26:36.100 line:80%
Qiu,

00:26:36.940 --> 00:26:38.460 line:80%
that's water under the bridge.

00:26:38.820 --> 00:26:40.220 line:80%
Why cling to the past

00:26:40.620 --> 00:26:41.860 line:80%
and slander Lord Yin Dai?

00:26:41.860 --> 00:26:43.300 line:80%
Slander him?

00:26:44.300 --> 00:26:45.500 line:80%
Everything I am today

00:26:46.740 --> 00:26:49.300 line:80%
is entirely thanks to him.

00:26:51.020 --> 00:26:52.700 line:80%
I lost back then; so be it.

00:26:53.260 --> 00:26:54.620 line:80%
I could have left.

00:26:55.380 --> 00:26:58.100 line:80%
But Yin deliberately sent me

00:26:58.100 --> 00:27:00.700 line:80%
to Youming Path to gather intel.

00:27:01.380 --> 00:27:04.500 line:80%
I was ambushed by the demonic sect
and almost died.

00:27:05.580 --> 00:27:08.260 line:80%
The fellow disciples
who promised to meet me

00:27:08.500 --> 00:27:10.540 line:80%
never showed up.

00:27:11.740 --> 00:27:13.980 line:80%
Yin feared I wouldn't submit

00:27:15.300 --> 00:27:18.380 line:80%
and wanted to use the demonic sect
to get rid of me

00:27:18.660 --> 00:27:20.340 line:80%
to clear the way

00:27:20.340 --> 00:27:22.780 line:80%
for his son-in-law and for himself.

00:27:23.060 --> 00:27:25.100 line:80%
You're just smearing my grandfather.

00:27:25.100 --> 00:27:26.020 line:80%
Do you have any proof?

00:27:26.260 --> 00:27:27.180 line:80%
Proof?

00:27:27.500 --> 00:27:30.060 line:80%
If your grandfather
were truly upright and selfless,

00:27:30.060 --> 00:27:32.740 line:80%
why did he steal Cai Pingshu's credit?

00:27:34.900 --> 00:27:35.780 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:27:37.020 --> 00:27:38.100 line:80%
What credit did he steal?

00:27:39.013 --> 00:27:40.020 line:80%
In the Battle of Mount Tu,

00:27:40.020 --> 00:27:42.500 line:80%
Cai Pingshu killed Nie Hengcheng.

00:27:42.660 --> 00:27:45.700 line:80%
Yet Yin Dai held a victory banquet

00:27:45.700 --> 00:27:48.540 line:80%
and claimed the merit for himself.

00:27:48.540 --> 00:27:50.340 line:80%
It was my aunt who killed Nie Hengcheng.

00:27:50.820 --> 00:27:51.900 line:80%
How did it become his doing?

00:27:53.060 --> 00:27:53.900 line:80%
That's right.

00:27:54.660 --> 00:27:57.220 line:80%
Everyone knew about the battle

00:27:57.220 --> 00:27:58.620 line:80%
between them.

00:28:00.980 --> 00:28:02.220 line:80%
That was later talk.

00:28:03.060 --> 00:28:04.500 line:80%
At the banquet back then,

00:28:04.860 --> 00:28:06.580 line:80%
it was Yang Yi, the Lord of Siqi Sect,

00:28:06.580 --> 00:28:07.540 line:80%
your grandfather,

00:28:07.540 --> 00:28:09.220 line:80%
who said it was Lord Yin Dai's merit.

00:28:09.380 --> 00:28:11.580 line:80%
Lord Yin Dai casually accepted it.

00:28:12.020 --> 00:28:13.780 line:80%
After that, everyone said

00:28:14.180 --> 00:28:16.900 line:80%
that Lord Yin Dai killed Nie Hengcheng.

00:28:20.180 --> 00:28:21.940 line:80%
But he didn't benefit for long.

00:28:22.220 --> 00:28:23.540 line:80%
Just a few months later,

00:28:23.660 --> 00:28:24.780 line:80%
Lord Yin Dai

00:28:24.780 --> 00:28:27.020 line:80%
was ambushed by Zhao Tianba,

00:28:27.020 --> 00:28:28.380 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng's first disciple,

00:28:28.500 --> 00:28:30.020 line:80%
and hacked to death.

00:28:30.020 --> 00:28:31.020 line:80%
And then?

00:28:31.180 --> 00:28:34.180 line:80%
Yin Qinglian feared being implicated.

00:28:34.460 --> 00:28:35.900 line:80%
To protect Yin Dai's grandchild,

00:28:35.900 --> 00:28:37.020 line:80%
her own son,

00:28:37.300 --> 00:28:38.820 line:80%
she diverted the calamity elsewhere

00:28:39.180 --> 00:28:41.780 line:80%
and leaked the news
that Cai Pingshu killed Nie Hengcheng

00:28:42.340 --> 00:28:43.740 line:80%
to the demonic sect.

00:28:44.100 --> 00:28:45.980 line:80%
No wonder they attacked Luoying Valley.

00:28:46.460 --> 00:28:48.300 line:80%
If not for Uncle Chang and Master

00:28:48.300 --> 00:28:49.500 line:80%
eliminating Zhao Tianba...

00:28:49.620 --> 00:28:52.060 line:80%
Luoying Valley would've been wiped out.

00:28:52.820 --> 00:28:53.780 line:80%
Afterward,

00:28:54.180 --> 00:28:56.180 line:80%
Yin Qinglian shamelessly claimed

00:28:56.420 --> 00:28:59.620 line:80%
that Lord Yin Dai
only reluctantly accepted

00:28:59.620 --> 00:29:02.180 line:80%
to protect Luoying Valley.

00:29:02.580 --> 00:29:04.380 line:80%
That even earned Yin

00:29:04.740 --> 00:29:07.740 line:80%
the title of the Pillar
of Righteousness.

00:29:08.380 --> 00:29:09.660 line:80%
Lady Qinglian

00:29:10.380 --> 00:29:11.500 line:80%
really had a sharp mind.

00:29:13.060 --> 00:29:13.900 line:80%
Today,

00:29:14.100 --> 00:29:15.940 line:80%
I will let these juniors

00:29:16.180 --> 00:29:18.100 line:80%
and the entire world know

00:29:18.100 --> 00:29:19.820 line:80%
the true face of Yin

00:29:19.820 --> 00:29:20.780 line:80%
and see

00:29:20.780 --> 00:29:22.980 line:80%
these hypocrites and frauds.

00:29:22.980 --> 00:29:23.820 line:80%
Qiu.

00:29:28.220 --> 00:29:29.940 line:80%
Please stop talking.

00:29:35.380 --> 00:29:37.620 line:80%
Even if Lord Yin Dai wronged you,

00:29:38.086 --> 00:29:39.420 line:80%
you colluded with the demonic sect

00:29:39.431 --> 00:29:40.889 line:80%
and harmed your fellow sect members.

00:29:40.900 --> 00:29:42.500 line:80%
Is that really not wrong?

00:29:47.660 --> 00:29:49.660 line:80%
I know my sins are grave.

00:29:51.340 --> 00:29:53.900 line:80%
When I was on the brink of death,

00:29:55.420 --> 00:29:57.300 line:80%
it was Nie Zhe who saved me.

00:29:59.260 --> 00:30:02.300 line:80%
A man lives for those who know him.

00:30:06.460 --> 00:30:08.900 line:80%
Even if I submit to the demonic sect,

00:30:10.500 --> 00:30:11.940 line:80%
so what?

00:30:11.940 --> 00:30:14.140 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:30:19.660 --> 00:30:20.940 line:80%
That's still better

00:30:23.340 --> 00:30:26.340 line:80%
than being deceived

00:30:28.660 --> 00:30:30.580 line:80%
and used.

00:30:34.500 --> 00:30:35.420 line:80%
Qiu,

00:30:36.100 --> 00:30:37.740 line:80%
I know you were misled by villains

00:30:37.740 --> 00:30:38.900 line:80%
and have your hardships.

00:30:39.500 --> 00:30:41.980 line:80%
Confess the demonic sect's later schemes

00:30:41.980 --> 00:30:42.980 line:80%
and make amends.

00:30:43.540 --> 00:30:44.980 line:80%
I can let bygones be bygones.

00:30:52.780 --> 00:30:55.060 line:80%
I can afford

00:30:56.860 --> 00:30:59.060 line:80%
to lose.

00:31:02.260 --> 00:31:03.300 line:80%
He'll kill himself!

00:31:12.020 --> 00:31:15.220 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:31:24.660 --> 00:31:25.500 line:80%
Mother!

00:31:25.700 --> 00:31:26.540 line:80%
Mother.

00:31:26.780 --> 00:31:27.620 line:80%
Mother!

00:31:28.020 --> 00:31:28.860 line:80%
Mother.

00:31:34.340 --> 00:31:41.260 line:80%
(Pillar of Righteousness)

00:31:52.060 --> 00:31:56.420 line:80%
(Pillar of Righteousness)

00:32:00.980 --> 00:32:03.380 line:80%
(Pillar of Righteousness)

00:32:05.300 --> 00:32:06.420 line:80%
I noticed long ago.

00:32:06.980 --> 00:32:08.820 line:80%
Gilded gold is the weakest.

00:32:14.940 --> 00:32:15.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:32:17.740 --> 00:32:18.860 line:80%
the Yins

00:32:19.980 --> 00:32:21.340 line:80%
owe Luoying Valley an apology.

00:32:22.700 --> 00:32:23.700 line:80%
You're different

00:32:24.740 --> 00:32:25.580 line:80%
from them.

00:32:46.300 --> 00:32:47.980 line:80%
When I was young, my aptitude was poor.

00:32:48.380 --> 00:32:49.660 line:80%
I could never break through.

00:32:50.780 --> 00:32:53.700 line:80%
Back then, this old friend
traveled through beaches and ravines,

00:32:53.900 --> 00:32:55.780 line:80%
deep into deserts and miasma forests,

00:32:56.340 --> 00:32:57.820 line:80%
risking countless dangers,

00:32:58.300 --> 00:33:01.620 line:80%
just to refine one Clearing Pill.

00:33:02.060 --> 00:33:03.420 line:80%
Your old friend

00:33:03.860 --> 00:33:05.300 line:80%
was truly thoughtful.

00:33:06.520 --> 00:33:11.710 line:80%
♪If we never met♪

00:33:12.990 --> 00:33:18.560 line:80%
♪Would there be no longing♪

00:33:19.560 --> 00:33:21.800 line:80%
♪In that fleeting moment♪

00:33:22.430 --> 00:33:25.430 line:80%
♪Within this lifetime♪

00:33:26.090 --> 00:33:28.340 line:80%
♪We already brushed past♪

00:33:29.500 --> 00:33:30.460 line:80%
I pray

00:33:31.420 --> 00:33:32.580 line:80%
to stay together forever

00:33:33.020 --> 00:33:34.180 line:80%
with Qiu.

00:33:39.160 --> 00:33:41.530 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:33:41.530 --> 00:33:45.850 line:80%
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

00:33:46.860 --> 00:33:48.380 line:80%
I pray to spend every day and night

00:33:49.180 --> 00:33:50.340 line:80%
with Sulian.

00:33:52.780 --> 00:33:55.390 line:80%
♪After parting♪

00:33:56.020 --> 00:33:58.340 line:80%
♪Before death♪

00:33:59.460 --> 00:34:04.330 line:80%
♪We meet no more♪

00:34:08.460 --> 00:34:10.500 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:34:14.300 --> 00:34:15.220 line:80%
Yunke.

00:34:31.040 --> 00:34:33.500 line:80%
♪Love and hate, scattered in threads♪

00:34:33.500 --> 00:34:37.690 line:80%
♪Intertwined and tangled into lines♪

00:34:38.300 --> 00:34:39.990 line:80%
♪With sandstorms filling the sky♪

00:34:39.990 --> 00:34:44.270 line:80%
♪I can still recognize your face♪

00:34:44.790 --> 00:34:47.550 line:80%
♪After this life♪

00:34:48.110 --> 00:34:50.440 line:80%
♪Before the next rebirth♪

00:34:51.430 --> 00:34:56.290 line:80%
♪We meet no more♪

00:34:56.860 --> 00:35:03.860 line:80%
♪I only wish to remember your face♪

00:35:06.260 --> 00:35:09.420 line:80%
(The turmoil within Qingque
has been settled.)

00:35:09.420 --> 00:35:13.100 line:80%
(Miss Cai is unharmed.)

00:35:19.780 --> 00:35:20.620 line:80%
Young Master,

00:35:20.780 --> 00:35:21.780 line:80%
they're here.

00:35:37.300 --> 00:35:39.580 line:80%
(Carefree)
Welcome back, Young Master.

00:35:40.780 --> 00:35:42.740 line:80%
I've waited anxiously for over a year;

00:35:42.740 --> 00:35:43.820 line:80%
at last, today has come.

00:35:44.420 --> 00:35:45.473 line:80%
(Carefree)
Over a year ago,

00:35:46.100 --> 00:35:49.220 line:80%
Elder Tianquan Qiu Baigang
aided my uprising, which failed.

00:35:50.300 --> 00:35:52.500 line:80%
Almost no one
from Elder Qiu's line survived.

00:35:53.220 --> 00:35:54.620 line:80%
I did not summon you before

00:35:54.980 --> 00:35:56.580 line:80%
because I could barely protect myself

00:35:56.860 --> 00:35:58.940 line:80%
and didn't want you to die with me.

00:35:59.940 --> 00:36:01.620 line:80%
Now that you've answered the call,

00:36:03.020 --> 00:36:04.300 line:80%
you surely know

00:36:04.820 --> 00:36:06.020 line:80%
what I intend to do.

00:36:06.479 --> 00:36:09.220 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng and his followers
usurped power for three generations.

00:36:09.460 --> 00:36:11.020 line:80%
Their influence runs deep and tangled.

00:36:11.540 --> 00:36:13.820 line:80%
Killing one or two
would never turn the tide.

00:36:14.340 --> 00:36:15.180 line:80%
So,

00:36:15.940 --> 00:36:18.460 line:80%
this journey will surely be full

00:36:18.980 --> 00:36:20.500 line:80%
of blood and corpses.

00:36:22.700 --> 00:36:24.060 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:36:25.100 --> 00:36:27.860 line:80%
Though the poison
of the Sevens Pill is fierce,

00:36:28.020 --> 00:36:29.220 line:80%
as long as you

00:36:29.540 --> 00:36:31.100 line:80%
are loyal to the Young Master,

00:36:31.340 --> 00:36:34.180 line:80%
the antidote will be delivered on time.

